Musician and actor Bonginkosi Dlamini, also known as Zola 7, is giving away bursaries for students who wish to study at the Afribiz Academy. Zola, together with the institution, aims to uplift and empower the youth. Afribiz Academy public relations manager Tameez Chothia said the bursary would cover all tuition costs. Chothia said,Â for many South African families tertiary education was a key to the future and great sacrifices were made to ensure that young people enjoyed study opportunities that were denied to their parents. -TNA Reporter